# Cursor Rules for Listick Project

## Code Style Rules

### Avoid withOpacity

- Do not use `withOpacity()` method calls in the codebase
- Instead, use predefined color constants or create new color variables
- This applies to all Flutter/Dart files in the project

### Alternative Approaches

- Use predefined theme colors with built-in opacity
- Create custom color constants with specific opacity values
- Use `Color.fromRGBO()` or `Color.fromARGB()` for custom opacity needs
